extends layout

block content
  h2 HAT Social Data Plug
  p.plug-info You can synchronize your Facebook data with your personal HAT and browse it on RUMPEL.
  p.plug-info
    span A few simple steps would get you going:
    ul
      li 1. Authorise the Plug to login to your Facebook account
      li 2. Select the categories for synchronization between HAT and Facebook
      li 3. See your data appear on RUMPEL

  .container
    a.plug-button(href="/dataplug") Start Here
    a.plug-button(href="http://www.hatdex.org") Learn more about your data